    <h2 class="title">  </h2>
    <div class="content">
      <h1 class="section-header"><img width="106" height="44" alt="What is the Commons?" src="/files/images/what-is-the-commons.gif"/></h1><p>Academic Commons is a  community of faculty, academic technologists, librarians, administrators, and other academic professionals interested in two interlocking questions: how do creative uses of new technology and networked information support the current project of liberal education, and, perhaps more interestingly, how do they force us to re-think what it means to be liberally educated? <a href="/about/about-academic-commons">Learn more.</a></p>    </div>    
